title: Khatarnak Khiladi
subTitle: A vegetable vendor takes care of an elderly woman and her two young daughters, but he has a dark past that wants to catch up with him.

title: Saptagiri Express
subTitle: A happy-go-lucky aspiring actor, who is forced to take up his father's job only to find out that his father's death was a planned murder.

title: Colors Cineplex
subTitle: Bringing the best in television.

title: Mere Baap Pehle Aap
subTitle: A man who runs a shopping centre must continually deal with his widowed father who is finding himself consistently being reprimanded by the local law enforcement officers.

title: Kabzaa - The Mafia Raaj
subTitle: Vijay Chandra, a determined police aspirant, battles a local MLA's corrupt efforts to seize his family's land. Joined by other wronged citizens, he takes a stand for justice and honor.

title: Jaanbaz Ki Jung
subTitle: An idle young man falls for a doctor who saved his mother. However, she asks him to kill a drug lord for her love, revealing her hidden revenge plot for her murdered family.

title: Fidaa
subTitle: Varun, an NRI medical student, and Bhanu, a vivacious young woman, fall in love with each other. However, they face many personal differences, creating complications in their relationship.

title: Chhaava
subTitle: Shivaji's death sparks the Maratha-Mughal conflict. His son Sambhaji leads resistance against Aurangzeb's forces. Amid battles and intrigue, both sides face challenges in a struggle for power.

title: DNA
subTitle: A new mum with BPD believes her baby was switched after birth. While others doubt her, her reformed addict husband races to find their real child before time runs out.

title: Diesel
subTitle: A driven young man gets ensnared in the dangerous web of the diesel mafia and is forced to confront ruthless and corrupt authorities.

title: Khaidi No. 150
subTitle: After escaping from prison, a criminal flees the country. Having spent his entire life on the wrong side of the law, he is suddenly move by the plight of farmers he meets there and fights for their cause.

title: Khaidi No. 150
subTitle: After escaping from prison, a criminal flees the country. Having spent his entire life on the wrong side of the law, he is suddenly move by the plight of farmers he meets there and fights for their cause.

title: RDX
subTitle: Robert, Dony and Xavier grow up together while honing their fighting skills. However, after an incident separates them for several years, an attack on their family reunites the three friends.

title: Sharafat Gayi Tel Lene
subTitle: A mysterious source deposits 100 crores into Prithvi's account. A top-notch henchman calls him asking him to deliver the sum to various places from time-to-time.

title: Angrezi Mein Kehte Hain
subTitle: When love goes flying out of the window, a middle-aged couple struggles to keep their lives together and rekindle their romance that was long buried under the burden of domestic responsibilities.

title: Ek Hi Maqsad
subTitle: Captain Ram is a military commando who rescues Patil, the tourism minister of Karnataka from Jihadi terrorists. Taking a liking for his heroics, Patil engages him to provide security.

title: Roberrt
subTitle: Raghava lives with his son and is the head cook in a Brahmin's catering unit. He lives peacefully, wanting the best for his son. All seems to go well, until some skeletons tumble out of his closet and he is forced to take on his original avatar.

title: Baaghi 2
subTitle: A battle-hardened army officer squares off against drug lords and Russian henchmen to save his ex-lover's kidnapped daughter in the underbelly of Goa, India.

title: Devaki Nandana Vasudeva
subTitle: Driven by fear of an astrological prophecy, Kamsa torments his sister's family, convinced her child will cause his downfall. When imprisoned, Krishna shields the family from Kamsa's sinister schemes.

title: Dumdaar Khiladi
subTitle: A middle class boy deeply loved by his family comes to Hyderabad from Kakinada for his IT job. He stays in the house of a family friend in the city and falls in love with his daughter.

title: Dashing CM Bharath
subTitle: Oxford graduate Bharat assumes his late father's role as chief minister. He strives to reform a corrupt society, but encounters fierce opposition from adversaries.

title: Shootout at Lokhandwala
subTitle: On a calm summer day in 1991, in the bustling Lokhandwala Complex, five criminals including Maya and Dilip were counting 70 lakhs in flat No 32B, when 286 policemen, headed by ACP Khan, took strategic positions around their building. A gunfire ensued and the entire nation witnessed the most talked about daylight encounter lasting 6 hours that transformed suburban Mumbai into a virtual war zone.

A gunfire ensued and the entire nation witnessed the most talked about daylight encounter lasting 6 hours that transformed suburban Mumbai into a virtual war zone.

title: Mahadev Ka Gorakhpur
subTitle: When evil descends chaotically upon the goodness of the land, a righteous warrior of Lord Shiva arrives to deliver justice to the wicked.

title: 1947: Earth
subTitle: The disaster of Indian/Pakistani partition seen through the eyes of a child - Lenny, an eight-year-old crippled girl - from Lahore, the Punjabi city that saw some of the bloodiest pogroms. The experiences, hopes and fears of this young girl provide an intense portrait of the period.

title: Pankh
subTitle: Film highlighting a phenomenon peculiar and exclusive to the Indian film industry, the practise of casting children in roles opposite to their natural genders.

title: Thadam
subTitle: Identical twins are taken into police custody in a murder case.

title: Theeran
subTitle: An honest police officer finds himself transferred again and again due to his sincerity. After his latest transfer, he comes across a file that involves a gang of ruthless thieves who loot and kill along the highway.

title: Rider
subTitle: As love blossoms between orphans Chinnu and Kitty, fate separates them as children. However, they grow up yearning to find each other.

title: Maragadha Naanayam
subTitle: Two small-time thieves who work for a jewel smuggler take up a contract to locate a cursed emerald medallion. With the help of a priest, they summon three spirits to guide them in their quest.

title: Tanhaji: The Unsung Warrior
subTitle: Subhedar Tanhaji, better known as Chhatrapati Shivaji's right-hand man, does whatever it takes to preserve the honour of the Marathas in a critical battle against Mughal chieftain Udaybhan Singh Rathore.

title: Motta Shiva Ketta Shiva
subTitle: Shivakumar, a dishonest cop, ensures that he is transferred to Chennai, where he exploits his position for financial gain. He also supports GK, a local MP, against the commissioner of Chennai.

title: Chithha
subTitle: Living a quiet life with his niece, Eeswaran manages to provide for her and nurtures her like a parent. However, his journey takes an insidious turn when she goes missing.
